text: Pogonocherus cedri is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Peyerimhoff in 1916. It is known from Algeria. It feeds on Cedrus atlantica and Abies numidica.BioLib.cz - Pogonocherus cedri. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 1916
